  <h1><a href="https://mylittlehouseontheinternet.neocities.org/guidelines" style="color: black; text-decoration:none;">guidelines: about</a></h1>
  <br>
  <p><b>Godelieve de Bree</b> is published by <em>Los Angleles Review of Books</em>, <em>The Poetry Review</em> and Tate. She is the pamphlet editor for <em>guidelines</em>.</p>
  <p><b>Olive Franklin</b> appears in <em>The Poetry Review</em>, <em>Poetry</em> and <em>Granta</em>. She is the magazine editor for <em>guidelines</em>.</p>
  <p><b><em>guidelines</em></b> is a publishing project putting out themed online issues of nine poems and one interview. Our print pamphlet series will open for submissions in early 2026.</p>
  <br>
  <p>contact: <a href="mailto:guidelinepress@gmail.com">guidelinespress@gmail.com</a></p>
